data.description: Welcome to this wonderful home that is move-in ready! Located in the heart of Grassfield, mins to I-64/168 by-pass. The Rome model is a 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath beautifully maintained home with scenic wooded views. A welcoming foyer leads to an entertaining open plan w/ crown molding/chair rail details throughout. The gourmet kitchen boasts tons of premium cabinetry and a large center island & bar with granite countertops. A convenient mudroom provides easy access to the 2-car garage. The luxurious owner's suite w/ a tray ceiling includes a sitting room, 2 walk-in closets and a private bathroom w/ a soaking tub, standalone shower and  dual vanity sinks. The newly paved patio is perfect for entertaining and enjoying the peaceful backyard. Home has 2 NEW HVAC systems/ductwork, plumbing & electrical.
